=== UK ME/CFS Biobank

The UK ME/CFS Biobank at UCL/Royal Free Hospital holds over 600 donors (ME/CFS, MS, and healthy controls) with more than 30,000 blood aliquots linked to clinical phenotyping data, including pain measures As Europe's first ME/CFS-specific biobank, it provides the infrastructure for correlating pain phenotypes with biological specimens.


